              h4 Support
              ul
                li
                  a(href="http://geometryzen.github.io/faq/", target="_blank")
                    | Frequently Asked Questions
                li
                  a(href="https://github.com/geometryzen/geometryzen/issues", target="_blank")
                    | Ask a Question
                li
                  a(href="javascript:;")
                    | Video Tutorial
                li
                  a(href="javascript:;")
                    | Feedback
                li
                  a(href="https://github.com/geometryzen/geometryzen/issues", target="_blank")
                    | Issue Tracker
